videos.headline: Missouri WR Moore extends Tigers' lead with excellent TD grab
videos.description: Missouri WR J'Mon Moore shows off excellent concentration making a touchdown catch with his fingertips on the sideline to extend the Tigers' lead over Delaware State.

videos.headline: Missouri's lead widens with Moore's second TD
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock finds J'Mon Moore for their second touchdown connection of the game to increase Missouri's lead over Delware State.

videos.headline: Daniel Epperson pass intercepted, Michael Scherer return  for 19 yds

videos.headline: Missouri WR Moore bullies his way into end zone for third TD
videos.description: Missouri WR J'Mon Moore forces his way through Delaware State's defense into the end zone for his third touchdown catch of the game.

videos.headline: The Lock-Moore TD connection strikes for a fourth time

videos.headline: Missouri blowout in full effect after 35-yard TD pass
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock finds Emanuel Hall for a 35-yard touchdown grab, giving the Tigers a 58-0 lead over Delaware State before halftime.

videos.headline: Missouri WR Moore puts on a touchdown show in first half
videos.description: Missouri WR J'Mon Moore could not be stopped by the Delaware State defense scoring four first half touchdowns en route to Missouri's 79-0 rout.
